Red Ice is a fast paced hockey game where you smash friends and foes alike while striving to be the best.

An in depth single player story mode lets you follow your favorite team
through a maze of mystery to unlock the hidden truth.

Multiplayer VS. Mode with up to 4 players. Use gamepads for best results.

Music by Aaron Cherof (http://cherof.com/)
Art by Brent Anderson (http://dumbmanex.com/)
Gameplay by Daniel X Moore (http://strd6.com/)

Minigames update coming soon.
